The paper deals with the problem of coordinating the actions of a team of robots with periodic communication capability executing an information gathering task. This involves multi-agent optimal decision-making with an information theoretic objective function, which suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), Robotics (cs.RO), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Information Theory (cs.IT).
